I have children of my own ♪</i>

161
00:08:21.637 --> 00:08:24.112
<i>♪ They ask their father ♪</i>

162
00:08:24.197 --> 00:08:26.547
<i>♪ "What will I be? ♪</i>

163
00:08:27.895 --> 00:08:30.202
<i>"Will I be pretty?" ♪</i>

164
